name: Lost#1 2°56’40"S//60°40’35"W
description:
Landing 2°56’40"S//60°40’35"W
These are the coordinates of my landing. I have arrived at this place by mistake, this cannot be the place. I don't know what happened, I just woke up here, I feel confused and hurt, but also terrified.
My forced landing was on something that I cannot describe with simple words, I feel that it breathes, it observes me, that it complains, that it yells at me. It is definitely alive.
I sense that it doesn't like my presence. I am trapped here and I fear for my life.
I hope this blog serves to come for me. Let it be soon, because I am certain that they will only find my corpse.
